  <brief_title>The Association of Miltefosine and Pentoxifylline to Treat Mucosal Leishmaniasis: A Clinical Trial in Brazil</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Association of Miltefosine and Pentoxifylline to Treat Mucosal Leishmaniasis: An Open-label, Randomized Clinical Trial in Brazil</official_title>
